OL,5, One of Wales' only ethnic minority head
OL,6, teachers has told of the racism she has
OL,7, experienced in her career in a bid to  
OL,8, bring about change.                    
OL,10,FReena Patel said she was called racist 
OL,11,Fnames by children when working as a    
OL,12,Fsupply teacher in Wales.               
OL,14,FShe said she was previously turned down
OL,15,Ffor a head teacher job and told she    
OL,16,F"didn't reflect the community".        
OL,18,FShe has begun work to make her school  
OL,19,Fanti-racist, starting with training for
OL,20,Fits predominantly white teachers.      
